$ Oracle: Data Guard Apply Services
@ apply services

  *Apply services* applies → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/redo-log-files[redo] from
  → development/databases/Oracle/High-Availability/Data-Guard#dg-primary-db[primary databases] to
  → development/databases/Oracle/High-Availability/Data-Guard#dg-standby-db[standby databases].

{ Methods

  There are two methods in which apply services operate:
    • Redo apply: uses *media recovery* on a *physical* standby database.
    • SQL apply: re-executes → development/databases/Oracle/SQL[sql statements] on a *logical* standby database.

}


sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/High-Availability/Data-Guard/
